data.title: Sands Split Grav Net to Rafters From Dish
data.description: Enable your teammates at A Main looking to take Sands control with this simple Grav Net line up, as it'll force Defenders in an unfavorable position or prevent them from swinging out the smoke effectively.

data.title: Tree to B Site Dice Grav Net
data.description: Enable your teammates with this Grav Net line up when executing the B Site, as it prevents Defenders from peeking and escaping.
